Ek baar bas iss song ka meaning padhna 
It's not just about the sailor
First meaning of this song describes the journey of an actual sailor. His adventures and his life in sea.
Second meaning describes our sailor journey in this sea called life in which we are sailing.

And some people are like, this song is not good, bekar lyrics hain, gaane me se male singer ko hata dena chahiye. 
If they think ki sirf Female singers se gaana chal jaata na 
They're the most stupid people. Bas Aditya aur Achint ko hata ke dekho 
This song will lose it's soul.
